com.mapbox.vision.visionevents.events

Class Image

  • com.mapbox.vision.visionevents.events.Image

  • public class Image

    Represents image with format and size width-height. Allows to retrieve bytes of image or bitmap.

    IMPORTANT : do not cache or store images retrieved from SDK. Data that it holds can be invalidated. Instead, if you need the data, call Image.getImageBitmap or Image.getImageBytes and use it.

    See Also:
    Image.getImageBitmap, Image.getImageBytes
